1. Install Synaptic (melhor ferramenta para instalar e procurar pacotes do Linux):
sudo apt-get install synaptic

2. Instalar LIngua Portuguesa p/Latex:
sudo apt-get install sudo texlive-lang-portuguese

3. Instalar Biber p/latex:
sudo apt-get install biber (Nota: textline-bibletex-extra)

